      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition, having been well-maintained and cared for by its previous owner. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is ready for many more miles of adventure. It's a reliable, solid choice for anyone looking for a quality ride that\u2019s been kept in great shape!",
